Cape Town - Twitter exploded with reaction to the news that Cyril Ramaphosa had won the ANC leadership race at the party's 54th national elective conference.  After a race that was nearly impossible to call, Ramaphosa clinched the title of party president with 2 440 votes, compared to Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma's 2 261. Users fired up their best tweets, and #CR17 was the top trend in South Africa within minutes. Here is a roundup of some of the funniest tweets: 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  